title: Two graphic T-shirts feature retro and sports-inspired designs, one with a "Stay" cowboy riding a horse and the other with a basketball team celebrating Eastern Conference champions 2024.
The t-shirts feature vibrant, playful, and nostalgic graphics inspired by summer, gaming, nature, and retro styles, with bold text, colorful illustrations, and trendy designs suitable for 2024.
A person models a pink graphic tee featuring the phrase "BEAUTY WITHIN" repeated with a prominent pink rose design, suggesting a popular trend for girls' graphic tees in 2024-2025.

A red graphic t-shirt with a colorful, distressed design featuring the words "SURF" and "VIC" along with "SUMMER TIME" underneath, surrounded by summer-related items like lemons, a straw hat, sneakers, and a small potted succulent, all on a light wooden floor.
